archimate:Capability.name: Human Resource Management
archimate:Capability.documentation: Ability to assess, mentor, compensate, terminate, and otherwise coordinate individuals who are or have been incorporated under a legal agreement that includes compensation and other benefits, on a temporary or permanent basis.
